r>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 14:05:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1695391545</ingested><modified> 2023-09-22T14:06:05+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1109" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-08/8e0afe60-11a3-11ed-b24b-3694cfbfb7e8" width="1971"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1109" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-08/8e0afe60-11a3-11ed-b24b-3694cfbfb7e8" width="1971"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Solo Stove]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Solo Stove Fire Pit 2.0]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Solo Stove Fire Pit 2.0]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Sony ZV-E1 review: The best vlogging camera to date, by a big margin]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>内容创作者已成为无反光镜相机行业的关键部分，索尼在 2020 年推出 ZV1 相机时全面拥抱了他们。此后，该公司在其 ZV 系列中增加了至少四种型号，最新的是 12 兆像素全画幅 ZV-E1——迄今为止功能最强大的型号。</p><p>它使用与售价 3,500 美元的 A7S III 相同的传感器，A7S III 是一款视频对焦相机，在低光条件下也是一个奇迹。然而，ZV-E1 的成本低了 1,300 美元，因此它当然缺少一些关键功能，如电子取景器 (EVF)、双高速卡插槽、机械快门和一些物理控件。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><core-commerce id="7f467e49361943ccbfc5bafec642cd68" data-type="product-list"></p><p>同时，ZV-E1还具有A7S III所缺乏的一些功能，足够令人惊讶。其中大部分属于人工智能领域，对于视频博主来说非常有用，例如自动取景、高级主题检测和动态稳定。结合传感器和人工智能功能，可以毫不夸张地说，这款相机既是迷你 A7S III，又是功能强大的视频博客相机。数量之多的进步也使其成为一项技术<em>杰作</em>。</p><h3><strong>身体</strong></h3><div id="5ee7736514cc43208f3da681a66a0ea4"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x7E1qTdIdnI?rel=0&amp;start=43" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p>传感器可能相同，但 ZV-E1 看起来与 A7S III 截然不同。机身没有索尼经典的 A7 式无反光镜外形，而是像 A6700 或全画幅 A7C 一样矮胖。它还明显更小，重量比 A7S III 轻三分之一（483 克），使其成为索尼迄今为止最小的全画幅相机。</p><p>索尼宣称它是由再生塑料制成的，这使得这款相机比 A7 系列便宜得多，而且抓地力也更差。握把也较小，但考虑到重量较轻，我仍然能够获得相当牢固的抓握力。尽管材质较低，但它防尘防潮。</p><p>正如我们在许多最新相机上看到的那样，有一个用于照片、视频以及慢速和快速的开关，并且每个开关都有自己的专用设置。它的顶部有一个突出的红色录制按钮，与索尼的其他无反光镜视频博客相机（APS-C ZV-E10）一样，它有一个用于支持变焦镜头的变焦摇杆，并且还可以与索尼的“数字变焦”功能配合使用。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89c85a31-53bc-11ee-a7ec-f01357b3ce2c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89c85a31-53bc-11ee-a7ec-f01357b3ce2c" style="height:1238px;width:2200px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机" data-uuid="f6c00b0b-4d01-343d-b115-1db14f1cdf7d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p>除此之外，与 A7S III 相比，它的结构显着精简。虽然它确实有一些视频博客专用按钮，例如“产品展示”和“背景散焦”，但顶部（背面）只有一个控制转盘，前面没有转盘 - 这使得在全手动模式下使用物理控制来操作相机变得很困难模式。</p><p>也就是说，ZV-E1 是索尼首款可完全使用触摸控制进行操作的相机之一。大多数关键设置（快门速度、光圈、ISO 等）都可以通过这种方式更改，它还允许您通过向左或向右滑动来调整显示设置。当然，LCD 屏幕完全适合视频博主，尽管 1,03 万点的分辨率有点低。</p><p> A7S III 的 944 万点 EVF 是市场上最好的，而 ZV-E1 则根本没有取景器。我在明亮的日子里拍摄时错过了这个功能，但 EVF 确实有一个“阳光”模式，可以自动将亮度调到最大。</p><core-slideshow data-slideshowid="28707193-4b32-4cc8-8c31-e5ba66978e06"/><p>它使用与索尼旗舰机型相同的电池，因此一次充电即可进行 95 分钟的 4K 30p 视频录制和 570 张照片。幸运的是，USB-C Gen 3.2 端口可让您在拍摄时充电，并且还支持高速传输。</p><p>除了耳机和麦克风端口之外，它还有一个微型而不是全尺寸的 HDMI 端口，这对于视频博客相机来说并不理想。它只有一个高速 UHS-II 卡插槽。奇怪的是，与 A7S III 相比，缺乏快速 CFexpress A 型插槽似乎并没有限制视频拍摄。</p><h3><strong>视频</strong></h3><p>正如您对基于功能强大的 A7S III 的相机所期望的那样，视频规格令人印象深刻。它可以以高达 60 fps 的速度处理 4K 超高清视频，尽管它是从 12 兆像素、4,240 x 2,832 传感器进行轻微超采样的，因此它的锐度略低于 A7 IV 等更高分辨率的索尼相机。由于最近的固件更新，它还可以以高达 120 fps 的速度拍摄原生 4K，无需超级采样。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b399b1-53bc-11ee-bd7f-733b8f7f36b1" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b399b1-53bc-11ee-bd7f-733b8f7f36b1" style="height:1238px;width:2200px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机" data-uuid="6e8ca73e-b09d-3d17-ace4-7a74fdd1f96b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p>您可以从高质量和低质量 MP4 longGOP 选项中进行选择，所有选项均具有高达 4:2:2 10 位颜色深度和 280 Mbps 数据速率。还有高达 4K 60p 和 4:2:2 10 位颜色的 I 模式，可提供更流畅的编辑体验，无需转码。该设置使用高达 600Mbps (60 fps) 的更高数据速率，因此需要昂贵的高速 V90 UHS-II 卡。</p><p>索尼的 S-Log3 将动态范围提高到 14 级以上，您可以使用索尼的 LUT 预览素材或安装自己的 LUT。如果您不想记录日志的麻烦，S-Cinetone 还可以提高动态范围，并且以后更容易调整和编辑。</p><p>过热怎么办？由于它缺乏 A7S III 的热功能，因此连续录制时间较短，特别是在 4K60 及以上时。在该模式下，预计不到一个小时，具体取决于外部温度。内容创建者可能对此表示同意，但事件拍摄者可能需要寻找其他地方。</p><h3><strong>自动对焦和人工智能</strong></h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b34b90-53bc-11ee-bf9e-08e2759eb8b7" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b34b90-53bc-11ee-bf9e-08e2759eb8b7" style="height:1238px;width:2200px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机" data-uuid="248e623f-c0d4-3a51-8eb2-149df30ccc20"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p>在自动对焦方面，ZV-E1 实际上胜过 A7S III。这是因为它使用了索尼在 A7R V 中引入的新型 AI 处理器，因此它的行为更像该型号 - 特别是在图像跟踪方面。</p><p>它现在可以跟踪人类的头部和身体，而不仅仅是面部和眼睛。除了人之外，它还有动物、鸟类、昆虫、汽车、飞机和火车的特定设置。不幸的是，它确实缺乏自动设置，因此它无法自动选择主题类型 - 您必须深入菜单并自己执行此操作。</p><p>拍摄对象跟踪为无反光镜相机设定了新的速度和可靠性标准，即使在拍摄对象快速移动的棘手环境中，也能始终如一地实现自动对焦。这对于经常独自工作的视频博主来说非常重要。 That said, even Sony&#39;s system isn&#39;t perfect, as it can occasionally lose a subject&#39;s eyes in busy backgrounds.</p><p> AI powers other features too. For example, the built-in microphone is now directional, and can automatically aim toward the front, rear or all around, based on subject detection.</p><p> A key AI feature lets you digitally zoom an extra 1.5 times without much noticeable loss in quality. It works with the zoom rocker, and unlike with past ZV implementations, includes full subject tracking. That ability to zoom smoothly and automatically scale the image powers other features as well </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b399b0-53bc-11ee-b5e3-40476192e37f" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89b399b0-53bc-11ee-b5e3-40476192e37f" style="height:1238px;width:2200px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机" data-uuid="c6d78d96-20e3-37f4-99da-4d5a41579b9b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p></p><p> That starts with the ZV-E1&#39;s in-body stabilization. Optical-only offers 5 stops, enough to smooth handheld video without much movement. Active stabilization considerably boosts performance, but adds a slight 1.1x crop. However, dynamic stabilization is new and quite remarkable. It adds a 1.3x crop, but can effectively remove bouncing from footsteps, making it like using a dedicated gimbal – albeit with some loss in sharpness. With that feature, the ZV-E1 is the first camera that can really match the smoothness of the latest GoPro action cams.</p><p> The digital zoom teams up with subject tracking on two other new features as well. One is the Framing Stabilizer, which crops into the image, steadies the shot and keeps the subject in the center of frame, allowing for dolly-like smoothness.</p><p> Auto Framing, meanwhile, gives the illusion of camera movement. It first digitally zooms into the subject, then tracks it within the frame. You can choose a small, medium or large crop, different tracking speeds and more. You can even send an uncropped video to HDMI so you have two versions.</p><p> It also carries vlogger-centric features seen on other ZV models, including Product Showcase and Auto Depth of Field. As before, the latter automatically defocuses the background by instantly opening the aperture as much as possible. Product Showcase, meanwhile, ignores eye detection and quickly shifts focus to any foreground object brought in front of the camera. Finally, Breathing Compensation uses a slight digital zoom to maintain constant framing when changing focus.</p><h3> <strong>Video Quality</strong> </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d985f8d0-5947-11ee-bff3-9cfd317e2f3f" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d985f8d0-5947-11ee-bff3-9cfd317e2f3f" style="height:2160px;width:3840px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机，遥遥领先" data-uuid="ecfcf508-e224-378f-83ed-5ac04bf95da5"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p> As mentioned, 4K 30p and 60p video is slightly softer than Sony&#39;s 30-megapixel A7 IV due to the lower resolution. On the plus side, the absence of pixel binning means no there&#39;s no aliasing or other ugly artifacts that can ruin a shot.</p><p> The other positive aspect is far less rolling shutter than the A7 IV at the full sensor width. That means you can make quick pans or film fast-moving subjects without worrying about skewed video.</p><p> Apart from sharpness, image quality is superb. It delivers nearly 15 stops of dynamic range in C-Log3 mode, up there with the best mirrorless cameras. That allows for plenty of detail in dark shadows and bright highlights, even on sunny or dark days. S-Log3 mode, meanwhile, gives editors room to tweak video. Sony&#39;s colors are accurate, though skin tones can lack the warmth I&#39;ve seen on Canon models.</p><p> The ZV-E1 can&#39;t be beat in low light. It has dual native ISOs at 640 and a whopping 12800. That allows for low-noise video all that way up to ISO 25,600, and manageable levels even at 51,200 – letting you shoot by moonlight or candlelight. In fact, Sony&#39;s FX3 cinema camera with the same sensor was recently used to shoot a feature film called <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://ymcinema.com/2023/07/19/the-creator-an-imax-movie-shot-entirely-on-the-sony-fx3"><em>The Creator</em></a> , specifically because it&#39;s so good in low light.</p><h3> <strong>Photography</strong></h3><core-slideshow data-slideshowid="b576bd29-a505-4bd7-a1ae-91b3795a548b"/><p> Since it doesn&#39;t have an EVF or mechanical shutter, I wouldn&#39;t recommend the ZV-E1 for photography alone. That said, like the A7S III, it&#39;s more than competent in a pinch.</p><p> The AF works just as well with photography, and has the same features and tracking modes. So you can count on this camera to grab sharp photos, even when shooting bursts at up to the maximum 10 fps or in low light. It&#39;s actually a pretty good street photography or travel camera, as it&#39;s small, silent and discreet. And with so little skew, I rarely missed the mechanical shutter.</p><p> Photo quality is outstanding, particularly in very low light. RAW images can easily be tweaked, even at high ISOs, and colors are accurate. The biggest drawback is again the lack of sharpness. That means there&#39;s not a lot of room to crop into photos later, so you&#39;ll want to get your framing right when you take the shot.</p><h3><strong>包起来</strong></h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89ccee10-53bc-11ee-bfba-94bdc7240932" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/89ccee10-53bc-11ee-bfba-94bdc7240932" style="height:1238px;width:2200px;" alt="索尼 ZV-E1 评测：迄今为止最好的视频博客相机" data-uuid="f00b8c54-c842-335e-bf9a-e8eba5dcd97f"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">史蒂夫·登特 (Steve Dent)</div></figure><p> With all that it can do, Sony&#39;s ZV-E1 is the best vlogging camera on the market and its rivals aren&#39;t even really close. It delivers everything creators need like 4K 120p video, high dynamic range, unbeatable low-light capability, great ergonomics, the best AF on the market and a boatload of useful AI features. The main drawback is a lack of sharpness — but that&#39;s only really noticeable if you&#39;re pixel peeping.</p><p> The ZV-E1 costs $2,200, so its rivals include the $2,200 Panasonic S5 IIx, the $2,500 Canon EOS R6 II and Sony&#39;s own $2,500 A7 IV. All of those cameras have sharper 4K video and electronic viewfinders, so they&#39;re better hybrid cameras for both photography and video</p><p> The ZV-E1 beats them in nearly every other way, though, while breaking new ground with its innovative AI features. If you&#39;re a content creator looking for a full-frame camera in that price range, I&#39;d highly recommend the ZV-E1.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/sony-zv-e1-review-the-best-vlogging-camera-to-date-by-a-big-margin-140055155.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sony-zv-e1-review-the-best-vlogging-camera-to-date-by-a-big-margin-140055155.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a734ee89-1bd6-4f81-bea1-d1c7f4a45afc</guid><dc:creator> Steve Dent</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 14:00:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1695393539</ingested><modified> 2023-09-22T14:39:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Cameras & Photography]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1350" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2df667d0-5946-11ee-8cf9-8dde065eaf74" width="2400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDA